nd K–12 teachers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aElectronic books. 0aPerformance poetry. 0aSpoken word poetry. 4aEducation : Education. 4aEducation : Educational Research. 4aGeneral Interest : Poetry. 4aLanguage Arts : English. 7aEDUCATION / Secondary.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143847024540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438470245423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438470245/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles